4）LiangP*,LanF*,LeeAS*,GongT,SanchezVF,WangY,DieckeS,SallamK,KnowlesJW,WangPJ,NguyenPK,BersDM,RobbinsRC,WuJC.Drugscreeningusingalibraryofhumaninducedpluripotentstemcellderivedcardiomyocytesrevealsdiseasespecificpatternsofcardiotoxicity.&nbsp;Circulation&nbsp;2013;127(16):1677-1691&nbsp;(由DanRoden和CharlesHong配发评论)(2013&nbsp;年度基础研究领域最佳论文)&nbsp;(*并列第一作者)
